{"tid":776611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔想成世比人睇唔起","createTime":"2018-08-12T08:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T11:30:49.000Z","uid":143481,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c43455614da5c3243f3284cd88d83560fd69305","tid":776611,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"我書又唔肯溫<br />\nGym又唔肯做<br />\n身又唔夠健康<br />\n但我都係繼續咁垃圾<br />\n由細到大都淨係得個樣<br />\n我最大既優點係個樣<br />\n最大既缺點都係得個樣<br />\n我唔想再成世做花瓶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲打可以救我"},{"pid":"9df7668095929e4d149c5690c8b3248fba3f152e","tid":776611,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"d644834a2138a2d770c4cd01341f3838ea88c5f8","tid":776611,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9df7668095929e4d149c5690c8b3248fba3f152e","tid":776611,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"大概係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/165002_6baf656558c8027d630719b7c239533c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F165002_6baf656558c8027d630719b7c239533c.png&h=cde09254&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"737a1db5002007afecb708cf7be688cfc148ce80","tid":776611,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd90b4afd3ff97d85ab29e1e5579914289415edf","tid":776611,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}